						               													<description>Knights of King Arthur is an adventure game for two or more players -- played with miniature figures -- which simulates the heroic combat of the Age of Chivalry. Here is a realistic game in which you lead an army of knights and men-at-arms as they pit sword against shield in a struggle for the throne of medieval England. It is your skill and strategy which will determine the outcome.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Knights of King Arthur is a simplified version of Heritage's Knights and Magick gaming system. This set is your introduction to the world of Adventure Gaming with miniature figures -- then as your interests and abilities grow, you can add to the set with extra figures from the Knights and Magick line and begin playing with the extra features in the advanced Knights and Magick Rules Set.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;description from the publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A Knights and Magick series game from Heritage USA's Paint 'N' Play line. The Paint 'N' Play games all feature Heritage miniatures along with paints and painting instructions. Knights of King Arthur also includes miniatures rules that allow you to fight out battles directly on the tabletop.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Additional contents include 14 metal miniature figures, paints, brush, &amp;quot;gaming die,&amp;quot; and a painting guide. Heritage sold additional 25mm &amp;quot;fantasy-historical&amp;quot; metal figures that could be used with the series games.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;&amp;mdash;user summary&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
